<figureCitation id="133F4EABFF92FFBCCB28FB71FD69B0A8" box="[608,727,1202,1228]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="8.[136,229,1927,1949]" captionTargetBox="[163,1417,203,1884]" captionTargetId="figure-24@8.[151,1436,187,1900]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 3. A–B: Euphorbia heterophylla. A. habit, B. branch with cyathia. C–E: Euphorbia hirta. C. habit, D. branch with cyathia, E. cyathium. F–H: Euphorbia hyssopifolia. F. habit, G. synflorescence, H. branch with cyathia. Photos: O.L.M. Silva." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5146141" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5146141/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="200">Fig. 3C–E</figureCitation>
